text:
The leaves done gone and fell, y'all...
This here place done got mighty lonesome, ain't it~
But now, even the trees with fallen leaves are beautiful.

Sho' 'nuff~
That there sunset and them trees... lookin' mighty cool~!

Ah,
And the rustling of fallen leaves with every step...
...The energetic voices of children even in the cold?

Hehe, yeah.
It's a good season.

Yeah, yeah, when it feels like real winter~
I start yearnin' for somethin' warm~
...Shall we stop by a ramen shop on the way back?

! Yuika, that's a darn good idea~!
If we go straight on home, we gonna freeze to the core~!
